    "description": {
        "en-US": "Please note that I will <strong>not</strong> distribute any updates via <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://addons.mozilla.org\">addons.mozilla.org</a> anymore. I do neither agree, nor support, nor do I wish to be associated with the decisions of Mozilla to:\n\n<ul>\t<li>...turn the addon ecosystem into a walled garden, disallowing and disabling the ability of the user to run any addon they might wish to run.</li>\t<li>...drop support for full-fledged addons and instead limit addons to a very, very limited WebExtensions API.</li>\nI will only distribute updates via the GitHub page.\n\nWith Firefox 57, to be released at the end of 2017, this addon will cease working because support for XUL addons will be dropped. The only workaround I can offer in this regard is to no update Firefox after 56 is released.</ul>"
    },
